#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:2
msgid "QTensor"
msgstr "QTensor"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :mod:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor` module defines the "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` class and related helpers for "
"representing and manipulating quantum states and operators in sparse "
"form."
msgstr ""
"El módulo :mod:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor` define la clase "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` y funciones auxiliares "
"relacionadas para representar y manipular estados cuánticos y operadores "
"en forma dispersa."

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:8
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` wraps a dense NumPy array or "
"SciPy sparse matrix into a CSR-format sparse matrix, and can represent:"
msgstr ""
"La clase :class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` envuelve un array denso "
"de NumPy o una matriz dispersa de SciPy en una matriz dispersa en formato"
" CSR y puede representar:"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:10
msgid "**Kets** (column vectors of shape ``(2**N, 1)``)"
msgstr "**Kets** (vectores columna de forma ``(2**N, 1)``)"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:11
msgid "**Bras** (row vectors of shape ``(1, 2**N)``)"
msgstr "**Bras** (vectores fila de forma ``(1, 2**N)``)"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:12
msgid ""
"**Operators / Density Matrices** (square matrices of shape ``(2**N, "
"2**N)``)"
msgstr ""
"**Operadores / Matrices de densidad** (matrices cuadradas de forma "
"``(2**N, 2**N)``)"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:13
msgid "**Scalars** (``(1, 1)`` matrices)"
msgstr "**Escalares** (matrices ``(1, 1)``)"

