msgstr ""
":meth:`.fidelity(other)<qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor.fidelity>`: calcula "
"la fidelidad entre dos estados cuánticos"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:137
msgid ""
":meth:`.probabilities()<qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor.probabilities>`: "
"compute the probability distribution of each state in the computational "
