msgstr ""
":meth:`.probabilities()<qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor.probabilities>`: "
"calcula la distribución de probabilidad de cada estado en la base "
"computacional"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:138
msgid ""
":meth:`.partial_trace(keep)<qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor.ptrace>`: "
