msgstr ""
":meth:`.partial_trace(keep)<qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor.ptrace>`: traza "
"parcial"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:139
msgid ""
":meth:`.reset_qubits(qubits)<qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor.reset_qubits>`:"
